tters to Allah is divorce.\u201d Source: Sunan Ab\u012b D\u0101w\u016bd 2172 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0652\u063a\u064e\u0636\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27302,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/03\/21\/exploitation-women-workers\/","url_meta":{"origin":2845,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Injustice: Exploitation of women, workers, animals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 21, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAmong the greatest of sins to Allah is that a man marries a woman and, when he fulfills his needs with her, he divorces her and leaves with her dowry. And that a man employs another\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21687,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/01\/19\/allah-silent-benefit\/","url_meta":{"origin":2845,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Silence: Allah is silent on matters for your benefit","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 19, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhat Allah has made lawful in his book is lawful, and what he has made unlawful is unlawful. Whatever he has remained silent upon, it is for your benefit, so accept benefit from Allah. Verily, Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33612,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/24\/jokes-nikah-talaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":2845,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Jokes: Not allowed to play about divorce, freedom","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Fadallah ibn \u2018Ubayd reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIt is not permissible to jest about three matters: divorce, marriage, and emancipation.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 780 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0641\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0635\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quo